    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This AP2-generation example represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the F22C1 inline-four, the powerplant delivers a linear power band with a seamless VTEC transition at 6,000 RPM. The 6-speed longitudinal gearbox remains crisp with perfect synchro engagement, feeding power through a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, featuring untouched double-wishbone suspension geometry and pristine bushings. This is a true collector-grade specimen with all original VIN tags present, zero oxidation on the undercarriage, and a cockpit that shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. A mechanically flawless icon for the discerning purist.",
