      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster with a mirror-like finish, entirely free from swirl marks, stone chips, or parking lot imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or bolster compression, and the interior retains its original scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized service centers. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade specimen that satisfies the most discerning eye. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a bespoke indoor car cover.",
